楚好,可以迫佢交代"},{"pid":"369464cbf3b5a9ea3c88f9e5449530ef2d799784","tid":1543214,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:08:24.000Z","msg":"6月9撤回同9月4撤回分別係邊呀?<br />\n分別在於：<br />\n<br />\n殉港手足：<br />\n熊家俊先生（25歲） - 15/12/2017<br />\n梁凌杰先生（35歲） - 15/6/2019<br />\n盧曉欣小姐（21歲） - 30/6/2019<br />\nZhita Wu（29歲） - 30/6/2019<br />\n麥小姐（28歲） - 3/7/2019<br />\n梅先生（32歲） - 5/7/2019<br />\n范先生（26歲） - 22/7/2019<br />\nCalvin 郭先生（25歲） - 27/8/2019<br />\n姬先生（16歲） - 2/9/2019 <br />\n何小姐（27歲） - 4/9/2019<br />\n10人離世<br />\n<br />\n還有：<br />\n4隻眼<br />\n2次地鐵恐襲<br />\n2人被刀手斬至重傷<br />\n超過100人被檢控<br />\n超過1000人被捕<br />\n受傷, 逃亡不計其數<br />\n<br />\n淨係計以上的分別, 已經好明顯。<br />\n還有整個警隊及制度的不公義已暴露。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkC3deC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkC3deC.jpg&h=34367fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D2LPVhj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD2LPVhj.jpg&h=35c3dac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C4TBAhk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC4TBAhk.jpg&h=05bdd3d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t8LoZ1q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft8LoZ1q.jpg&h=fac47d55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ZTBFS9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ZTBFS9.jpg&h=3e1d2264&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dde863efcba4fab17bdc031d97275aa3f42cfaca","tid":1543214,"uid":197492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:08:25.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"4ebd3bdd4920b4223ffd2d86c2f69d99f5b95745","tid":1543214,"uid":105353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T09:48:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"327d8f5f4c8a81d9bc58a1f74f2ca9fbc4179a01","tid":1543214,"uid":179817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T09:51:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13501719acddce0bbb5fb6446805ae6e38d3440f","tid":1543214,"uid":75777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:18:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n官地丫拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黑社會丫拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cddd832ae31a85a6bd9890b23ecf034d0d2d71ac","tid":1543214,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad30607971f0f7a0ab3c5434dea64e7b0dcba32","tid":1543214,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"331d0973ffe83b244eaf4804d3a9b93033b417a5","tid":1543214,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:14:35.000Z","msg":"舊post : 南邊圍停車場係官地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1495211\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1495211</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nX：<br />\n<br />\n主旨： 投訴元朗站近南邊圍懷疑霸佔官地並擅自改作私人土地  (檔案編號：2-5603319364)<br />\n<br />\n就你2019年8月22日的投訴個案，地政總署已完成跟進有關南邊圍懷疑霸佔官地並擅自改作私人土地的事宜，現回覆如下：<br />\n<br />\n「元朗地政處經實地視察後<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">，確認查詢的南邊圍土地有被非法佔用政府土地情況</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，遂根據《土地(雜項條文)條例》(第28章)，在所涉的政府土地張貼通知，飭令佔用人於<span style=\"color: red;\">限期前</span>停止佔用政府土地，否則會採取進一步土地管制行動，包括移除涉事政府土地上的構築物和物品。此外，就上址有違例泊車的情況，地政處已將個案轉介部門作適當跟進。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">至於就違例泊車事宜，我們經審視後已轉介香港警務處跟進。當有跟進結</span>果，會盡快回覆你。<br />\n<br />\n如有任何查詢，歡迎與我們的職員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n1823<br />\n客戶服務主任<br />\nXXX謹覆  <br />\n2019年9月4日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來真係官地<br />\n大家搭開車就影下相放上來, 我繼續用返個File No.跟進!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n就違例泊車事宜，我們經審視後已轉介香港警務處跟進<br />\n元朗寸金尺土, 違泊真係好阻人, 大家見到有違泊就唔好放過, 打999, 元朗報案室都得, 打到有人到場為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:35:14.000Z","msg":"搵埋申訴專員公署"},{"pid":"f466ef621c43b3bce6409d7f4f233235db84c994","tid":1543214,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:37:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38f17e1a5465d9635d4b0f6a4189de8b58904751","tid":1543214,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:39:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f816e32574eccde8e70b9a1cc8ff3a2eef263ac","tid":1543214,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bcc60de527bbaf17b74e7626c0c7b379747ff2e","tid":1543214,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:58:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df6d7d479d58c8926e454da48ea080b7e1134f32","tid":1543214,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT